&lt;p&gt;The Orthopaedic and Fracture clinic are looking for a motivated and enthusiastic Band 2 full time Receptionist to support the existing Orthopaedic Receptionist Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will have excellent keyboard, &amp; interpersonal skills, be confident to work on their own initiative yet keen to be part of a larger team. If you think that you meet this job description, have a good sense of humour and would like to be part of this very busy department, then this could be the job for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Training &amp; support will be provided in this rewarding role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details please contact Lin Bryant, Orthopaedic Outpatient Manager on 01225 825653 or e-mail linda.bryant1@nhs.net.or Alison Coles on 01225 826104 or e-mail alisoncoles@nhs.net.&lt;/p&gt;
